      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Recommended Storage Environments</title>
         <div class="- topic/div ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">The
recommendation are for storage in the transportation crates with the
sealed inner packing.</p>
            <ul class="- topic/ul ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">Storage temperature:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
                     <li class="- topic/li ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Battery: See recommendations from the original equipment manufacturer
(OEM).</p>
                     </li>
                     <li class="- topic/li ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">System: -10 °C to +55 °C (+14 °F to +131 °F)<fn class="- topic/fn ">For aluminum foil vacuum sealed packing with indicator instruments
the storage temperature is +5 °C to +60 °C (+41 °F
to +140 °F).</fn>
                        </p>
                     </li>
                  </ul>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Relative humidity: 0–95% Non-condensing</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </div>
